41:16.546 --> 41:18.969
The Bible says today is a day of salvation.

41:19.049 --> 41:20.510
I wanna give you that opportunity.

41:21.031 --> 41:26.477
You may have just stumbled on this broadcast by accident, but it's no accident because God got you here.

41:26.957 --> 41:30.301
So I wanna get you to pray this simple prayer.

41:30.741 --> 41:35.427
And if you meet in your heart, you can be saved and have your way to heaven.

41:35.507 --> 41:37.008
Just say this and mean it.

41:37.369 --> 41:43.355
Say, dear God, I believe Jesus died on the cross from my sins.

41:44.056 --> 41:45.938
I believe Jesus

41:46.114 --> 41:48.199
was raised in the dead to save me.

41:48.941 --> 41:52.750
Jesus, I receive you as my Lord and Savior.

41:53.271 --> 41:59.506
Thank you for saving me, and Heavenly Father, fill me with your Holy Spirit in Jesus' name.

42:00.162 --> 42:00.643
Amen.

42:00.763 --> 42:02.848
If you prayed that for the first time, we believe you got born again.

42:02.908 --> 42:05.413
Thank you for praying that.

42:05.513 --> 42:08.820
And if you don't have a church home, come on out.

42:08.880 --> 42:10.223
Be a part of a sea life church.

42:10.283 --> 42:14.051
If you're here in the area, not in the area, find a good church home so you can grow in Christ.

42:14.371 --> 42:17.438
Continue to stay connected with a sea life church.

42:17.718 --> 42:18.840
And we'll see you next week.

42:18.901 --> 42:19.602
God bless you.

